reviewText: incredible series that I wish lasted longer.

I had so much fun watching this with my boyfriend. He had good memories of the show from the 90's, and it completely delivered. It can get a bit gross at timenot quite at the level of Ren & Stimpy, but along the same spectrumbut if you have a strong stomach, it will be fine! The DVDs worked great. The only reason I'm not giving it five stars is that the box, though very visually appealing, dents easily, and there are no subtitles on the DVDs.

Dvds are awesome all perfect condition and tin is cool looking only thing that I think customers should know is that there is a little velvet insert inside the tin and then the 6 DVDS are just stacked on top of each other, probably not good for keeping them from getting scratched so just so you know.

Was thrilled to add this to the "I Don't Need Cable Collection"  Purchased this set for myself and sat down to watch the Tallest and the Armada take on Zim. Great show from Nicktoons and really good to have the tin collector case as well.
The mighty DVDs of DOOM!! I love this show. The collectible tin was missing from my nerd hoard, and now I feel contented. For now... Until there's a new something.
Super good, it arrived august 1 , it said it would arrive in august 12 so im so happy , great price, A+

I was a little taken aback when this package came, and the outside said it was region 4.  But it appears that it does not have any encryption and it works just fine with my player.

This is a very fun series.
